  description: "Fairies are mischievous little creatures. They often take the form
    of small beautiful women, frogs, insects or simply be invisible. \nThey are the
    fog over the field at dawn and dusk - when they are said to dance freely. \n\nThey
    blow sickness on humans, so be guarded.  "
